average of 30 industrials rose 10.67 at 2,083.04.
   Bond prices finished higher in light dealings.
   The dollar finished mostly higher against other major currencies.
   Cotton futures prices soared, while prices for future delivery
of oil and oil products, grains, soybeans, copper, gold, silver and
livestock all finished higher.
