<2ND_LINE>PM-Wall Street Noon,0350</2ND_LINE>
<DATELINE>NEW YORK (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   The stock market edged upward today in a
lukewarm response to better-than-expected news on international
trade.
   The Dow Jones average of 30 industrials, up about 15 points in
the early going, showed a 3.20 gain at 2,086.24 by noontime on Wall
